WEBVTT

00:05.480 --> 00:07.658
Thanks for picking me up from work.

00:08.397 --> 00:09.896
No problem.

00:10.766 --> 00:12.199
Do me a favor, little brother.

00:12.201 --> 00:14.635
Pull over up there.
I need to cash my paycheck.

00:14.637 --> 00:16.770
You think it's still open?
It's kind of late.

00:16.772 --> 00:18.472
Trust me, it's open.

00:18.474 --> 00:19.906
Just pull over.

00:19.908 --> 00:21.880
And wait in the car.

